## Quoted Fields

### Embedded Commas

```javascript
const csv = `name,address,phone
Alice,"123 Main St, Suite 100",555-1234
Bob,"456 Oak Ave, Apt 5B",555-5678
Charlie,"789 Elm Rd, Building 3, Floor 2",555-9999`;

const result = parseCSV(csv);

