## Custom Configuration

### Different Delimiters

```javascript
// Tab-separated values
const tsvData = `name\tage\temail
John\t30\tjohn@example.com
Jane\t25\tjane@example.com`;

const result1 = parseCSV(tsvData, { delimiter: '\t' });
console.log(result1.rows[0].name);  // 'John'

// Semicolon-separated (common in some regions)
const csvData = `name;age;email
John;30;john@example.com
Jane;25;jane@example.com`;

const result2 = parseCSV(csvData, { delimiter: ';' });
console.log(result2.rows[0].name);  // 'John'

// Pipe-separated
const pipeData = `name|age|email
John|30|john@example.com
Jane|25|jane@example.com`;

const result3 = parseCSV(pipeData, { delimiter: '|' });
console.log(result3.rows[0].name);  // 'John'
```

### Different Quote Characters

```javascript
// Using single quotes instead of double
const csv = `name,address,phone
John,'123 Main St, Apt 4',555-1234
Jane,'456 Oak Ave, Suite 100',555-5678`;

const result = parseCSV(csv, { quoteChar: "'" });
console.log(result.rows[0].address);
// '123 Main St, Apt 4'

// Using backticks (for SQL-like syntax)
const sqlData = `name,description
Item1,`This is, "special" data`
Item2,`Normal text``;

const result2 = parseCSV(sqlData, { quoteChar: '`' });
```

### Custom Line Separators

```javascript
// Carriage return only (old Mac style)
const macData = `name,age\rJohn,30\rJane,25`;
const result1 = parseCSV(macData, { lineSeparator: '\r' });

// CRLF (Windows style)
const windowsData = `name,age\r\nJohn,30\r\nJane,25`;
const result2 = parseCSV(windowsData, { lineSeparator: '\r\n' });

// Custom separator
const customData = `name,age|John,30|Jane,25`;
const result3 = parseCSV(customData, { lineSeparator: '|' });

console.log(result1.rows.length);   // 2
console.log(result2.rows.length);   // 2
console.log(result3.rows.length);   // 2
```

### Combined Options

```javascript
const csv = `name;address;phone
John;'123 Main St, Suite 100';555-1234
Jane;'456 Oak Ave, Apt 5B';555-5678`;

const result = parseCSV(csv, {
  delimiter: ';',
  quoteChar: "'",
  lineSeparator: '\n'
});

console.log(result.rows[0].address);
// '123 Main St, Suite 100'
```

