## Aggregation

### Sum

```javascript
const csv = `product,quantity,price,total
Widget,100,19.99,1999
Gadget,50,29.99,1499.50
Tool,200,9.99,1998
Device,75,99.00,7425`;

const result = parseCSV(csv);

// Total revenue
const totalRevenue = result.sum('total');
console.log(`Total Revenue: $${totalRevenue.toFixed(2)}`);
// Total Revenue: $12921.50

// Total units
const totalUnits = result.sum('quantity');
console.log(`Total Units: ${totalUnits}`);
// Total Units: 425

// Sum on filtered data
const expensiveProducts = result
  .filter(row => row.price > 20)
  .sum('total');
console.log(`Expensive Products Revenue: $${expensiveProducts.toFixed(2)}`);
// Expensive Products Revenue: $8924.50
```

### Average

```javascript
const csv = `student,exam1,exam2,exam3
Alice,90,88,92
Bob,78,82,85
Charlie,95,91,93
Diana,87,89,86`;

